[{"id":919045,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p>去年秋天公司无了。我单身，就自己一个人一直在出租屋坐到现在，感觉自己精神状况和身体状况真的很差。已经分不清白天和夜晚了，日常肠胃出问题，早上起来舌头很厚，中间还有一条裂缝。昨天白天坐在电脑前还心悸了一下，甚至出门倒垃圾还出现了幻觉，甚至有时候自己和自己对话，说完才反应过来，自己也吓一跳。感觉精神分裂了。即使状态再差但是一点也不瞌睡，有时候 20 多个小时才会有想睡的感觉或者强迫自己躺下，躺下来却睡不着，不看手机也睡不着。也想过找工作，但是不知道是拖延症还是什么东西，似乎内心在等一个大事件或者什么节点来促使我变化,在此之前就摆烂等着。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919045","replies":105,"created_ts":1677276423,"created":"06:07:03","title":"失业半年多后感觉整个人状态非常差","author":"96","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/96","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/22ec/b4aa/613123_mini.png?m=1677044085"},{"id":919083,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119","description":"<p>抽了点时间重写了这个扩展，核心功能基本保留，一些用途不大或者目前已经实现不了的功能被移除，也增加了几个有意思的新功能，具体介绍可以看扩展的选项页面（应用市场的截图还是之前的版本，会尽快更新）。</p>\n<p>功能简介：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>通知功能：更新提醒、未读消息</li>\n<li>登录态判断：未登录 icon 提醒</li>\n<li>半小时自动签到</li>\n<li>主题列表预览及忽略功能</li>\n<li>新窗口浏览主题</li>\n<li>快捷键打开 V 站</li>\n<li>快捷键查看未读消息</li>\n<li>悬浮头像查看用户基础信息</li>\n<li>评论悬浮 @用户查看最近回复</li>\n<li>高亮楼主回复</li>\n<li>高亮回复感谢爱心</li>\n<li>会话详情（关联对话）</li>\n<li>回复指定用户添加楼层号</li>\n<li>划词 base64 解码</li>\n<li>评论发图 imgur 图床</li>\n<li>表情</li>\n<li>标记用户：高亮头像</li>\n<li>淡化注册时间一个月内的用户</li>\n<li>管理标记用户列表</li>\n<li>管理屏蔽用户列表</li>\n<li>管理忽略主题列表</li>\n<li>折叠超长主题、回复</li>\n<li>翻页自动跳过主题至回复</li>\n<li>修复历史微博图片显示</li>\n<li>集成 sov2ex</li>\n</ul>\n<p>安装地址：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/v2ex-plus/daeclijmnojoemooblcbfeeceopnkolo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chrome Webstore</a></li>\n<li>其他浏览器正在陆续更新适配</li>\n</ul>\n<p>其他：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Github： <a href=\"https://github.com/sciooga/v2ex-plus\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/sciooga/v2ex-plus</a> 欢迎 PR 、Star</li>\n<li>反馈： <a href=\"mailto:sciooga@gmail.com\">sciooga@gmail.com</a></li>\n<li>感谢 <a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/member/GPU\" rel=\"nofollow\">GPU</a> 共同维护及发布扩展</li>\n<li>感谢设计师 <a href=\"http://sheephe.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sheep</a> 设计 Logo</li>\n<li>感谢各位贡献代码、反馈建议、帮忙测试的小伙伴</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919083","replies":66,"created_ts":1677294716,"created":"11:11:56","title":"V2EX Plus 扩展升级到 2.0 版本了","author":"sciooga","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/sciooga","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2121/8e48/97098_mini.png?m=1676539170"},{"id":919144,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919144","replies":60,"created_ts":1677316665,"created":"17:17:45","title":"想用的名字 .com .net 都被注册了， .org 适合用来做商业产品吗？面向国外的产品，不能,备,案无所谓，刚注册了 10 年。本来想用 .cc .app 这样的非主流后缀，但产品面向的是不了解技术的用户，怕他们看不出来这是域名。","author":"edis0n0","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/edis0n0","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8acfb030e98c7c3f424344dfb6eb8512?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919165,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"今年九月份就要面临退伍了，现在很迷茫，家里的意思都想让我留在这，我自己是的想法是退的占多，V 站的老哥们帮忙给点建议吧","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919165","replies":59,"created_ts":1677326281,"created":"19:58:01","title":"退伍还是留队","author":"Mieuxx","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Mieuxx","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ce7a/1926/484532_mini.png?m=1587131404"},{"id":919096,"node":"YouTube","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/youtube","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ea5d/2f1c/64_mini.png?m=1630578528","description":"<div class=\"embedded_video_wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iadn-hOwvZc\" class=\"embedded_video\" allowfullscreen=\"\" type=\"text/html\" id=\"ytplayer\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div><br />Channel:<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@ymsy9898\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.youtube.com/@ymsy9898</a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919096","replies":57,"created_ts":1677298368,"created":"12:12:48","title":"YouTube 这类视频里的语音是 AI 么？","author":"Livid","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Livid","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_mini.png?m=1677298349"},{"id":919050,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>本来是去收个显卡，没想到怎么最后捡了个垃圾桶：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSemN9\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSemN9.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSemN9.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>以前经常在隔壁办公室看到，可惜开发方向不一样，一直也没申请搞个玩。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNHOI\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNHOI.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNHOI.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>这做工和质感，只能说不愧是当初 $3000 起的东西，巨厚的不锈钢外壳还能压成这模样，而且居然还有消指纹的镀膜，把玩后不会留下指纹印：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXUimq\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXUimq.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXUimq.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>Assembed in USA：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXUplj\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXUplj.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXUplj.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>什么 Mac Studio ，不过是丢人显眼的增肥 mini ，这才叫爹的工艺巅峰：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXU96s\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXU96s.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXU96s.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>时隔这么久还是第一次拆开看内部，只需要打开锁扣即可：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXwqgg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXwqgg.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXwqgg.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>内部依然一丝不苟：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXUF00\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXUF00.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXUF00.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>这极致的对称美学：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNqmt\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNqmt.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNqmt.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>内存分两边排布，构成四通道：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNxfg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNxfg.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNxfg.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>四条 8G 2R rank DDR3 ECC 内存构成的 4 通道 32G 容量，最高可以到 128G：\n当然也是 Micron 为 Apple 定制，标签都换成了黑色\n<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNvtS\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNvtS.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNvtS.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>掀开盖头，双显卡基板+ CPU 主板 + 内置电源：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXUCXn\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXUCXn.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXUCXn.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>其中一张显卡，上面是 SSD 插槽，可以升级到 2T ，而且不同于现在，那时候的苹果还有廉耻，不过就是 nvme 换插槽，轻松转接 nvme：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNjk8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNjk8.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNjk8.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>搞了个 Apple 转 Nvme 插头，再找个了闲置的 HP EX950 和 Thermalright 的 SSD 散热器：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSeljK\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSeljK.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSeljK.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>安装好散热器的 SSD </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSeQc6\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSeQc6.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSeQc6.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>替换上新的 SSD：\n<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSetNd\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSetNd.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSetNd.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>D500 显卡基板，性能大约就是 HD 7950/GTX670 水平，亮个机还是可以：\n<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNOTf\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNOTf.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNOTf.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>顶部巨大的风扇：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXNL0P\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXNL0P.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXNL0P.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>IO 指示灯，开机自动点亮，现在的 Apple 还会管你这些细节？</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/pSXN76A\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"pSXN76A.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/20/pSXN76A.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>通过 USB 重装系统，然后再 Time Machine 还原备份的系统：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSeK91\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSeK91.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSeK91.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>重新进入系统，一切恢复如常</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSed3t\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSed3t.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSed3t.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>SSD 从 512G 增加到 2T：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSeN4A\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSeN4A.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSeN4A.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>升级前的 SSD 测速：\n<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSewgP\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSewgP.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSewgP.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>升级后的 SSD 测速：\n<a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSe0jf\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSe0jf.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSe0jf.png\"/></a></p>\n<p>不过这台机器倒是有个好处，内存巨大，SSD 可扩充对于不那么吃 CPU 的应用，反而需要大量空间的用户，还是有自己的优势。</p>\n<p>总的来说 $400 就能感受到 10 年前的 Apple 巅峰，还想什么呢，毕竟按照如今 Apple 的价格，$400 也就够把内存从 16G 升级到 32G ，或者把 SSD 从 1T 升级到 2T 而已。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/ppSeM1x\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ppSeM1x.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/24/ppSeM1x.jpg\"/></a></p>\n<p>这几天用下来，真的感觉如果是开发的话，Mac Pro 确实蛮好用的，性能虽然差了 M1 Pro 一点，具体在 unit test ，M1 Pro 大概跑 1 分半，这个要跑 2 分半，但是两倍大的内存可以多开几个资源大的 docker 和 vm 而不用担心内存 swap ，x86 的工具支持度依然好过 Arm ，尤其是虚拟机方面。另外完全彻底的安静让你几乎感觉不到存在。另外如果还有更强的需求可以手动换用 10-12 核心的 Xeon ，多核性能还能再提升一点。而如果你的开发需要大量内存，最多支持 128G 内存量大管饱。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919050","replies":57,"created_ts":1677282783,"created":"07:53:03","title":"$400 收的垃圾桶，感觉捡到宝了，想把自己的 M1 Pro 换去垃圾桶","author":"privater","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/privater","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/88ec9b167e0455b97086f89a84625724?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919140,"node":"Go 编程语言","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/go","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_mini.png?m=1658910399","description":"<p>gorilla 已经不维护了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919140","replies":46,"created_ts":1677314934,"created":"16:48:54","title":"golang 的哪个 websocket 好用？","author":"dw2693734d","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dw2693734d","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_mini.png?m=1673068981"},{"id":919070,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","description":"<p>在家里，WiFi 连接一段时间后就断网了，断开 WiFi 再连接又恢复正常，现在在公司连 WiFi 是正常的没有问题，在家里其他手机包括其他三星也是正常的，这是个什么问题呢，有没有人知道</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919070","replies":45,"created_ts":1677290927,"created":"10:08:47","title":"新买的三星 S23 ultra 遇到一个问题，没有头绪","author":"kylelau","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kylelau","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/392cbee609891e20ea49bc633b9a8de0?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919133,"node":"Java","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/java","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/03af/dbd6/63_mini.png?m=1644490200","description":"<p>一个 Spring Boot 程序，占用内存 11G ，包大小 1G ，哭晕啊</p>\n<p>大家都是怎么瘦身的啊</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919133","replies":40,"created_ts":1677311530,"created":"15:52:10","title":"SpringBoot 的应用程序实在太大了","author":"GTim","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/GTim","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/525990ffd29f785f4c53b8f157389cc3?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919091,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"<p>目前手机有接近 2w 张照片，系统 13.7 ，mac 系统 12.6.2</p>\n<p>1.在 mac 下，我用自带的图像捕捉软件，手机照片选择保留原片，导入时，如果选择全部导入，100%会出错，表现在软件界面左边转圈，中间显示空白，需要部分多次导入，即使选择了部分，也有概率出错，如果手机照片选择自动，mojave 系统必出错，提示...文件未导入。 而且导入后查看，还有部分文件会漏掉</p>\n<p>2.win 系统照片应用 导入也有 bug ，导入到一半就报错了，而且是手机选择保留原片，选择自动的话 报错更快，而且所有导入的文件日期都改了 8 个小时时差</p>\n<p>3.win 直接复制 也会半路提醒报错</p>\n<p>4.现在尝试用 imazing ，感觉效果还行，就是不能保留照片的 aac 文件</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919091","replies":37,"created_ts":1677297198,"created":"11:53:18","title":"iPhone 照片原图导入电脑太难了","author":"luckyapple","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/luckyapple","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d5a9d6af8d44c515eef5401deb2e915?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919054,"node":"旅行","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/travel","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_mini.png?m=1608240651","description":"在元旦的时候，我去了一趟广西北海。<br /><br />有一天，我在北海金滩散步，结束了以后，<br />打开地图，看到地图上有写，旁边有一个叫做高德小镇的地方，<br />是一个旅游景点。<br /><br />就扫码一辆共享电动车，骑上就沿着海边的路去高德小镇。<br /><br />中途路过一个桥，桥不太高，很新的桥梁。<br /><br />慢悠悠的往上骑，在桥上，非机动车道停着一辆电动车，<br />旁边人行道站着两个年轻小伙子。<br /><br />到目前为止还是一切正常，继续骑行，<br />走近他们，我随便瞥了一眼，<br />继续骑行，走远 10 米的时候，<br /><br />我大脑忽然反应过来，我刚刚看到了什么：<br />地上一大摊血迹！！！<br /><br />猛的刹住，回头一看，<br />是的，没有看错。<br /><br />地上一大摊新鲜血迹，其中一个小伙，右手整个不见了，<br />穿着米色羽绒服，从手腕处垂下来丝丝缕缕的东西，<br />还在滴血，羽绒服袖口也有血。<br /><br />他左手拿着手机，不知道是在打电话还是。<br />脸上并无焦急神色，反倒是很淡然，那种平平无奇的样子。<br /><br />他的同伴稍稍背对着他，有点儿不敢看他。<br /><br />两个小伙很年轻，大概也就 16 、17 岁的样子。<br /><br />我大脑里面一方面想上前询问出了什么事要不要帮助，<br />但是不由自主的转动车把往前走了。<br />面对这恐怖事情还是有点儿想逃避。<br /><br />一路上，我都有点儿被震惊到了，<br />出了什么事？<br />有没有报警？<br />这右手不见了还能医治嘛？<br />能恢复到什么程度呢？<br />他年纪这么小，以后的生活该怎么办？<br /><br />就这样到了高德小镇，才发现整个小镇还在休整，并未对外开放。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919054","replies":37,"created_ts":1677285846,"created":"08:44:06","title":"记一次旅行中遇到的奇怪经历","author":"18115692244","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/18115692244","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9724/7ccf/213686_mini.png?m=1677284630"},{"id":919130,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<h1>intro</h1>\n<p>想写一写博客但是有一些痛点问题没有好的解决方法，所以想来请教一下大佬们</p>\n<h1>question</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n1.文字不足以描述时需要配插图，可是 <code>没有好的工具</code> 操作就变成以下步骤<ul>\n<li>1.1 截图</li>\n<li>1.2 重命名保存截图</li>\n<li>1.3 把截图放到指定静态资源文件夹</li>\n<li>1.4 使用 markdown 语法导入图片</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n2.一般来说带后台服务的博客有自己的在线编辑器，可以直接 cc cv 然后图就插好了，可是静态博客怎么办呢？<ul>\n<li>2.1 图片越多项目越大</li>\n<li>2.2 使用图床(目前没有找到可以白嫖或者便宜的每月付费制的图床)</li>\n<li>2.3 结合图床怎么才能实现 cv 之后直接传到图床, 然后 markdown 编辑器直接是链接形式的图片呢(目前没有找到一个合适的编辑器-可以结合没找到的图床的)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>想请教请教大佬们有没有具体的解决方案</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919130","replies":35,"created_ts":1677310525,"created":"15:35:25","title":"Q: 大家使用 Markdown 写静态博客的时候是如何插入图片素材的？","author":"anonymous2351d00","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/anonymous2351d00","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8cb65a0fef9be8f4c5cd6bcd3ddd2a61?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919068,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"希望他不知道就是不知道，而不是胡说八道，给一个完全错误的回答。<br /><br />比如 <br /><br />问：下面这篇文章的标题是什么? <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9416834\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9416834</a> <br /><br />回答：这篇文章的标题是 \"Neural Networks-Based Multi-Objective Control for a Hybrid Renewable Energy System with Energy Storage\"，发表在 IEEE Transactions on Industrial Electronics 期刊上。<br /><br />然而， 事实上并不是他说的这个标题， 而且他说的这篇文章并不存在。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919068","replies":35,"created_ts":1677289639,"created":"09:47:19","title":"不是调侃，有办法不让 chatgpt 胡说八道么？","author":"fengleiyidao","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fengleiyidao","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/68e8/2222/249538_mini.png?m=1673826796"},{"id":919163,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p>如题.玩过一点 python 和 go,都是个人感觉学起来和写起来都比较舒适的语言.\n而目前似乎很多公司用的仍然是 java,所以这三个语言对于新手来说优先学谁比较好?或者说有其他建议?</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919163","replies":33,"created_ts":1677325095,"created":"19:38:15","title":"新人入门后端,目前优先学什么语言好","author":"acherkrau","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/acherkrau","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/861a77fd243d0843ce4e70e7cb9a03a8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919114,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1673261684","description":"<p>以前查字典， 比如 hang 字典中有几十种意思。 不知道上下文中是什么意思， 字典中一个个看意思，在结合上下文去测，很浪费时间，有时还不知道什么意思。\n下面这句话我开始不懂 hang 的意思 Only in the last hour had Harry really got the hang of the Summoning Charm.</p>\n<p>然后问 chagGPT:\n请用中文告诉我， 下面这句英语中『 Only in the last hour had Harry really got the hang of the Summoning Charm.』 hang 是什么意思？</p>\n<p>chatGPT：\n在这句英语中，“hang” 是一个动词，意思是掌握或理解某个技能或知识。整句话的意思是：直到最近一小时，哈利才真正掌握了召唤咒语。</p>\n<p>但是现在的痛点是每一个单词在句中的意思都要先打这么一句话，才能得到答案。不能取词 如果现有的英语字典。 比如欧路词典 或者 有道词典。 能智能的根据上下文。如 chatGPT 一样 生成单词多个意思中最接近上下文的意思。而不是给出一大堆意思，让你自己选一个。这会大大缩短查词时间。 就会是一个词典的智能革命。。</p>\n<p>如果不是做词典的。 有人能写一个油猴脚本吗？ 划词时，把单词所在的句子一起生成 prompt 然后向 chatGPT 提交，然后让 chatGPT 返回解释。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919114","replies":33,"created_ts":1677305832,"created":"14:17:12","title":"英语字典革命，谁来做个 chatGPT 英语字典","author":"z7356995","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/z7356995","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/244ff0bb7793a0c2725c298c77d71e27?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":919131,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>i5/i7 6200/7200/8200 8GB</p>\n<p>求问下各位老哥，这个配置能流畅办公么？</p>\n<p>Office 三件套，聊天软件（微信），腾讯会议，浏览器，偶尔简单的图片处理。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919131","replies":31,"created_ts":1677311173,"created":"15:46:13","title":"XPS 13 CPU 6/7/8 代 i5 8GB 内存现在能流畅办公么","author":"panlatent","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/panlatent","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d30b/8fb4/90818_mini.png?m=1663317782"},{"id":919109,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>也学过不少语言了，rust 、go 、python ，总是学完语法，不能完成一个项目，看开源项目，感觉也很难看进去，没办法达成编程能力的进阶。</p>\n<p>有啥好办法能够突破初学这一层呢</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919109","replies":30,"created_ts":1677304112,"created":"13:48:32","title":"大家如何实现编程能力的进阶，从学习完语法到能够写项目","author":"proxytoworld","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/proxytoworld","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5e55/4696/481415_mini.png?m=1651761065"},{"id":919176,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1670739760","description":"<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/25/pppe9R1.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>之前不知道为啥 B 站老推广他的视频，点击看过，表情呆滞，照本宣科；项目算是入门级别的吧\n但一如既往的孜孜不倦的录。</p>\n<p>后面浏览星球的时候无疑中发现，这个 id 和头像很熟悉</p>\n<p><img alt=\"img\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/02/25/pppeSi9.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>这样一年就差不多 500w 到手了。</p>\n<p>比上班好多了。。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919176","replies":29,"created_ts":1677332054,"created":"21:34:14","title":"你们真的以为 B 站大 V 靠点击率 接广告为生的么？","author":"yagamil","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yagamil","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e322/1a6d/318767_mini.png?m=1612024295"},{"id":919150,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>前端用 Vue 框架搭建的，生成一串密钥保存在 .env 里</p>\n<p>使用 hashids 把用户密码加密保存到 localStorage ，在登录界面 取出密文用 hashids 解密，再自动填充到 password 中。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>这种情况下，攻击者如何取出并解密得到用户的密码？</li>\n<li>前端应该如何保存密码或者 token 来实现免登录？</li>\n</ol>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/919150","replies":25,"created_ts":1677318783,"created":"17:53:03","title":"如何破解前端保存的用户密码？","author":"yjim","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yjim","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7d0dd77cae4da5bbaa09f25cbc7b1cd3?s=24&d=retro"}]